  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The use of MDS to access the presence of melanoma in the skin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A topical agent is applied to suspicious skin lesions and imaged. The images are analyzed to
      provide a score that correlates with the probability for the presence of melanoma in the
      lesion.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
